# Testing

- Commands: `client/venv/bin/python -m pytest tests/ -q`; `cd ui && npm run build`.
- Do not weaken tests to pass; do not hide failures.
- New auth/size/state fixes need negative tests (401/409/413).
- Prefer regression tests for restart durability and idempotency when touching those paths.
- Integration shell scripts under `tests/integration/` may be stale — verify `DATASET_PATH` assumptions.
